<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로드의 전술서:신고내역</title>
    <link href="../sources/img/로전아이콘.svg" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon">


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.13.1/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    
        <%- include('../nav_and_banner.ejs', {page: 'admin', nickname: data.nickname, notice:data.banner_notice }) %> 



    <form class="container mt-5">
        <h3 class=""><신고 내역></h3>
        <p class="color-red">
            지정 후 버튼 누르면 일괄 적용. 종료일은 정지 처분 시에 지정됨. 정지 지정 후 종료일 지정 안할 시 1달 뒤로 자동 지정.
            <br> 중복 대상에 대한 처분 시, 가장 강력한 것 기준으로 진행. (삭제+정지 > 정지만/삭제만 > 처분 안함 > 나중에)
            <br> 정지만 및 삭제만이 공존 시, 삭제 + 가장 긴 기간 정지
        </p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger mt-2 mb-2">저장하기</button>
        <table class="table w-100 table-bordered table-striped">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="28px">id</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="120px">신고자</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2">신고 이유</th>
                    <th scope="col" rowspan="2" width="120px">대상 작성자</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">대상 컨텐츠</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">신고당한 횟수</th>
                    <th scope="col" colspan="2">처분</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" width="100px">종류</th>
                    <th scope="col">내용</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="55px">작성자</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="55px">컨텐츠</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="90px">종류</th>
                    <th scope="col" width="110px">종료일</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% for(let i=0; i<data.report_data.length; i++){ %>
                <tr class="position-relative">
                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%=data.report_data[i].id%>">
                    <th scope="row"><%= data.report_data[i].id%></th>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].USERNAME%></td>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].reason%></td>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].object_user%></td>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].object_kind%></td>
                    <td class="object" data-obid=""><a href="/forum/share/detail/<%=data.report_data[i].link_id%>" target="_blank"> <%= data.report_data[i].object_body%> </a></td>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].user_cnt%></td>
                    <td><%= data.report_data[i].content_cnt%></td>
                    <td><input readonly name="how" style="width: 80px;" value="나중에">
                        <ul class="report-dropdown" style="display: none;">
                            <li>삭제만</li>
                            <li>정지만</li>
                            <li>삭제+정지</li>
                            <li>처분 안함</li>
                            <li>나중에</li>
                        </ul>
                    </td>
                    <td><input type="date" name="end_date" ></td>
                </tr>
                <% } %>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </form>
   


    

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <script>

    $(document).on("click", function(e){
        if(!$(e.target).closest("input[name='how']").length>0
        && !$(e.target).closest(".report-dropdown li").length>0
        ){
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
            
        }
    })
    $("input[name='how']").on("click active", function(e){
        if(this.nextElementSibling.style.display == 'none'){
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
            $(this).siblings(".report-dropdown").slideToggle();
        } else{
            $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
        }
    })

    $(".report-dropdown li").on("click active", function(e){
        $(".report-dropdown").slideUp();
        $(this).parent().siblings("input").val($(this).text())
    })
    </script>
</body>
</html>